sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>MLConfigPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>MLConfigView
    participant SER as MLModelConfigSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Set confidence threshold value
    FE->>API: PATCH /api/ml/config/ {confidence_threshold: 0.85}
    API->>DB: MLModelConfig.objects.get(environment=env)
    DB-->>API: MLModelConfig instance
    API->>SER: MLModelConfigSerializer.validate(data)
    API->>DB: config.confidence_threshold = 0.85
    API->>DB: config.save()
    DB-->>API: Config updated
    API-->>FE: 200 OK {confidence_threshold: 0.85}
    FE-->>U: Threshold updated, alerts below 85% confidence suppressed
